                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-08-21</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很浅易的行文，配图很珍贵，对了解台湾印刷史有帮助。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1115498037">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1115498037" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1115498037" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1115498037">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4203678/">Grace</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-01</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">满有劲的一本书，台湾对传统文化的保护与传承意识比大陆做得好太多，当然日本做得更好。我们这只有一家字模一厂，还是传统的国企做派，算上青浦独立出来的，也就勉强两家，相较下差多了。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
